headline: Raymond James Announces Quarterly Dividend
summary: On May 21, Raymond James Financial, Inc. (NYSE:RJF) announced a quarterly cash dividend of $0.50 per share, payable on July 15, 2025, to shareholders recorded as of July 1, 2025. The financial services giant’s Q2 2025 net revenues reached $3.40 billion, up 9% year-over-year. For the first half of fiscal 2025, the company posted record […]
